The paper presents a solution for the localization and mapping problem using 3D point clouds, which is a common topic in robotics (cs.RO). The method is based on extracting segments and using data-driven descriptors, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the extraction of semantic information, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
